thread.title: Keegan Tolman
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Keegan Tolman

author: Keegan Tolman
title: Keegan Tolman
text:
I have been using Ink Stations Epson compatible ink for over a year now. I buy a 10 pack of Epson compatible ink from InkStation which costs $88.48.
On the Epson Website ordering the same ink cartridges but as genuine Epson ink, comes to $547.90! that's more then we paid for our printer and I have never had a problem with Ink Stations inks. and although our warranty with Epson is now void, if anything did happen, the amount we've saved would more then pay for a new printer. I highly recommend!!
